    <comment>New package skillspector (security scanner for AI agent skills) + -mcp subpackage. Resubmit of the declined SR 1362984: source now comes from a reproducible obs_scm git snapshot of upstream main (2.3.9~git20260701.326a2b48, commit 326a2b48) because NVIDIA/skillspector publishes no git tags, no GitHub releases and nothing on PyPI. source_validator passes. Final piece of the langchain/langgraph cone: requires langchain-core, langgraph, langsmith&gt;=0.7.30 etc. Please co-stage with the sibling devel:languages:python cone SRs by pluskalm (Staging:adi:38) and python-langsmith (SR 1362932, science:machinelearning-&gt;Factory) or the build is unresolvable. Builds clean (noarch, 0 rpmlint badness, %check 1249 passed) where the stack is available.</comment>
